<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Business Phase Unlock Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <p>Hi {{studentName}},</p>

      <p>
        We're pleased to inform you that the
        {{phaseName}}
        phase in your TruPreneurs.AI journey has been unlocked.
      </p>
      <p>You can now access this phase for your businesses and take the next step towards shaping your business idea. </p>

      <p>Best Regards,<br />TruPreneurs.AI</p>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
      &copy;
      {{year}}
      TruPreneurs.AI. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </body>
</html>